leads.lead_text: Leaves cylindric, narrow; flowers solitary or paired on wiry flowering stem, not resupinate (i.e. labellum uppermost in flower); mid-lobe of labellum prominently wavy and crisped

Leaves thick and leathery, or thin, flat, ovate to broadly elliptic or narrow-elliptic to narrow-obovate; flowers numerous on stiff raceme, flowers resupinate (i.e. labellum lowermost in flower); mid-lobe of labellum entire
Inflorescences 20–70 cm long, 20–115-flowered; perianth segments narrow-linear
Inflorescences 5–17 cm long, 2–15-flowered; perianth segments broad
